							he says. Brhaspati is the holy power (Brahman) of the gods; verily he
							grasps hold of him, and he brings him safely through. 'Here we have
							come (a-idam) to the place on earth for sacrifice to the gods', he
							says, for he comes to the place on earth for sacrifice, who sacrifices.
