							calms his pain; with three (verses) he pours (it) down, Agni is three
							fold; verily he calms Agni's pain throughout his whole extent. 'Mitra
							having united the earth', he says; Mitra is the auspicious one of the
							gods; verily; and also (it serves) for support. He hands (the pan) over
