							equal girth with Prajapati, the beginning of the sacrifice. He makes it
							with two breasts, for the milking of sky and earth; he makes it of four
							breasts, for the milking of cattle; he makes it of eight breasts, for
							the milking of the metres. For him who practises witchcraft he should
